div><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects__item">Ilmu Ekonomi</div><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects__item">Biologi</div><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects__item">Ilmu Politik</div><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects__item">Ilmu Komunikasi</div><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects__item">Ilmu Administrasi</div><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects__item">Ilmu Hukum</div><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects__item">Akuntansi</div><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects__item">Agribisnis</div><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects__item">Ilmu Lingkungan</div></div></div><div class="jsx-1801937352 faculty-item__icon"><svg class="icon" name="next"><use xlink:href="#common-next"></use></svg></div></a><a href="https://campus.quipper.com/directory/universitas-riau/faculties/fakultas-hukum" class="jsx-1801937352 faculty-item"><div class="jsx-1801937352 faculty-item__content"><h6 class="jsx-1801937352 faculty-item__name m-b">Fakultas Hukum</h6><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects"><div class="jsx-3706647023 faculty-subjects__item">Ilmu Hukum</div></div></div><div class="jsx-1801937352 faculty-item__icon"><svg class="icon" name="next"><use xlink:href="#common-next"></use></svg></div></a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="registration" class="jsx-3088077293 school-registration"><div class="jsx-3455656720 campus-section"><div class="jsx-3428262767 cmps-container"><div class="jsx-2684177403 section-title"><h2 class="jsx-2048192465 Typography text-variant-headline">Pendaftaran</h2></div><div class="jsx-4000830923 cmps-content-wrapper"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Berikut​ ​informasi​ ​seleksi​ ​masuk​ ​yang​ ​dapat​ ​Quipperian​ jadikan ​​bahan​ ​rujukan​ ​jika​ ​kalian menjadikan​ ​Unri sebagai ​pilihan​ untuk melanjutkan​ ​studi selanjutnya!​</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
